description._content: Description: Top seven terraces in Machera Forest, planted with Cypress trees in December, 1921, View in April, 1927, Five seasons later than No. 52. Location: Cyprus Date: 1927 Description: A long series of terraces made in 1922 and 1923 in Machera Forest, on the Western side of the Yiallias Valley, showing development by the year 1927, Elevation about 4,000 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1927 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
